{"tid":1282572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Anonymous呼籲","createTime":"2019-07-03T15:14:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T15:27:21.000Z","uid":120119,"like":54,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9a55ed6f3095c647a574f1d8a3eca1c817c95286","tid":1282572,"uid":120119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:14:48.000Z","msg":"Whatsapp 各通訊軟件受到中國黑客攻擊入侵，大多人因此不能下載圖片影片及聽取錄音，請注意自己whatsapp及個人手機上有否敏感消息圖片及文字，我們anonymous會為香港各位打贏呢場仗，we are anonymous we are legion we do not forgive we do not forget expect us！"},{"pid":"a70fcb87a8a8d66e54b2569e22da54a8506615fc","tid":1282572,"uid":264792,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:15:14.000Z","msg":"來源？"},{"pid":"6784c91a254808bd8df12f748f6a706473173182","tid":1282572,"uid":240713,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:15:17.000Z","msg":"係咪真？"},{"pid":"bb67ce709f62f4a2c1f03d7ca9d01575e411508e","tid":1282572,"uid":258513,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:15:41.000Z","msg":"唔怪得下載唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"216638d4b2333f3f764d64145d531664234f9b39","tid":1282572,"uid":259675,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:15:53.000Z","msg":"Source ?"},{"pid":"d28a5ad20d4709ac80b53ea86fe423d652b186af","tid":1282572,"uid":80072,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:16:11.000Z","msg":"Anonymous = Netsand之輩<br />\n無須再推佢嘅嘢<br />\n真嘅駭會自己做嘢<br />\n會咁撚得閒tweet埋呢d嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2014咪見識過&ldquo;佢&rdquo;啲本事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07f58ae7fe87347d1c495d